{
  "stem": "27150.8",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was 8 bob apiece, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] so it was 40 pounds, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] you know.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I got a little place in 430 Bourke Street.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, I put up a table and a sewing machine, and I made 100 of those belts.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this fellow put on 100% and sold it to Myer's, you see.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I said, I can do it myself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so I started a belt factory, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it's a funny thing, you see, I was going, and then I said that I did something in leather for Myer's.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But you see, the main business in belts were covered belts for the manufacturers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And a friend of our friends had gave me some work to [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to cover belts, and-- and that's where it started, you know.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It means, I couldn't manage the electric machine, but somehow I was-- I was doing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And at that time, everything goes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I went to the Jewish manufacturers to support me, and a fellow I met in a place-- and I spoke to him English.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I didn't know he was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He was a Warsaw Jew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I met him at the German-- Jewish German office.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I spoke to him English.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then one day, I come to a Jewish customer, a woman, who was running a frock shop, to pick up merchandise.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I met him in the hall, and I started to speak English.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You see, with him, that's just normal, just like I spoke to everybody in Shanghai and after.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And she just walks in, and he said, look at him, he already speaks English.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He said, you see when we came, you couldn't stay a word, and this and that and that.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
